    <entry>
      <title>测试公式</title>
      <link href="/2020/01/13/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/"/>
      <url>/2020/01/13/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&lt; –!more– &gt;</p><h2 id="测试公式"><a href="#测试公式" class="headerlink" title="测试公式"></a>测试公式</h2><h3 id="公式位置"><a href="#公式位置" class="headerlink" title="公式位置"></a>公式位置</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$f(x)&#x3D;ax+b$</span><br><span class="line">$$f(x)&#x3D;ax+b$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>前段文字$f(x)=ax+b$后段文字。</p><p>前一行文字$$f(x)=ax+b$$后一行文字？</p><h3 id="上下标"><a href="#上下标" class="headerlink" title="上下标"></a>上下标</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$f(x) &#x3D; a_1x^n + a_2x^&#123;n-1&#125; + a_3x^&#123;n-2&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$f(x)=a_1x^n+a_2x^{n-1}$$</p><h4 id="左右都有上下标"><a href="#左右都有上下标" class="headerlink" title="左右都有上下标"></a>左右都有上下标</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$\sideset&#123;^n_k&#125;&#123;^x_y&#125;a$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$\sideset{^n_k}{^x_y}a$$</p><h3 id="括号"><a href="#括号" class="headerlink" title="括号"></a>括号</h3><p><strong>需要转义！</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\&#123;x*y\&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>{x*y}</p><h4 id="符号缩放"><a href="#符号缩放" class="headerlink" title="符号缩放"></a>符号缩放</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$\left \lbrace \sum_&#123;i&#x3D;0&#125;^n i^3 &#x3D; \frac&#123;(n^2+n)(n+6)&#125;&#123;9&#125; \right \rbrace$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$\left { \sum_{i=0}^n i^3 =\frac{(n^2+n)(n+6)}{9} \right }$$</p><h3 id="分数-开方"><a href="#分数-开方" class="headerlink" title="分数/开方"></a>分数/开方</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\frac xy$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\frac xy$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$x+3 \over y+5$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$x+3 \over y+5$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\sqrt&#123;x^5&#125;$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\sqrt{x^5}$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\sqrt [3]&#123;\frac xy&#125;$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\sqrt [3]{\frac xy}$</p><h3 id="求和与积分"><a href="#求和与积分" class="headerlink" title="求和与积分"></a>求和与积分</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\sum_&#123;i&#x3D;0&#125;^n$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\sum_{i=0}^n$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\int_1^\infty $</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\int_1^\infty$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\iint_1^\infty$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\iint_1^\infty$</p><h3 id="极限"><a href="#极限" class="headerlink" title="极限"></a>极限</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\lim_&#123;x \to 0&#125;$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\lim_{x \to 0}$</p><h3 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$\begin&#123;array&#125;&#123;c|lcr&#125;</span><br><span class="line">n &amp; \text&#123;Left&#125; &amp; \text&#123;Center&#125; &amp; \text&#123;Right&#125; \\\\</span><br><span class="line">\hline</span><br><span class="line">1 &amp; 1.97 &amp; 5 &amp; 12 \\\\</span><br><span class="line">2 &amp; -11 &amp; 19 &amp; -80 \\\\</span><br><span class="line">3 &amp; 70 &amp; 209 &amp; 1+i \\\\</span><br><span class="line">\end&#123;array&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$\begin{array}{c|lcr}n &amp; \text{Left} &amp; \text{Center} &amp; \text{Right} \\\hline1 &amp; 1.97 &amp; 5 &amp; 12 \\2 &amp; -11 &amp; 19 &amp; -80 \\3 &amp; 70 &amp; 209 &amp; 1+i \\\end{array}$$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">名称|说明</span><br><span class="line">---|---|---</span><br><span class="line">temperature|  室内温度</span><br><span class="line">set temperature|  设定温度</span><br><span class="line">height|  室内高度</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Link:<a href="http://stevenshi.me/2017/06/26/hexo-insert-formula/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://stevenshi.me/2017/06/26/hexo-insert-formula/</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
